document_data.Notable Champions:
* [[Hyustus Staget]], a member of the [[Waterdhavian]] [[City Watch (Waterdeep)|City Watch]] and patrolman of the city's [[Waterdeep/Dock Ward|Dock Ward]].{{Cite adventurers league/Unsafe Harborage|4}}
* [[Galwain|Sir Galwain]], a member of the [[Hellriders]] who was interred within the [[Tomb of Trials]].{{Cite adventurers league/In the Hand|6}}
* [[Portia Dzuth]], the surviving member of a Waterdhavian [[adventurer|adventuring company]] who originally hailed from [[Rashemen]].
* [[Sekelok]], the [[yuan-ti pureblood]] champion of [[Ras Nsi]].
